name: SXZ Blizzard Style [ Warcraft & Hearthstone ]
description:
All the content I make is and will be completely free on CivitAI.
But if you want to support me with a coin, then you can do it here.

Trained on AbyssOrangeMix2 with clip skip 2.

Recommended embeddings:
1. easynegative
2. bad-hands-5

Strength 1 - 0.6 is optimal.

PLEASE CHECK YOUR LORA NAME AFTER DOWNLOAD.

Trigger word isn't necessary. Also i highly reccomend to use this tags volumetric lighting, best quality, masterpiece, intricate details in the end of your prompt.

Enjoy and share your feedback.

modelVersions.name: sxz-blizz-v2
modelVersions.description:
+111 pics in dataset

Minor noise offset tweak.

More consistent style not only for characters but for environment and objects too.
